overview:
Music social networks for artist to share their music and videos through facebook, and twitter instantly.

Through this site, you will be able to have your song uploaded and spread out using Twitter,Facebook and all the other Social networking sites out there,The site Features an Interface that lets you choose what you want to share ( song/Full Mixtape or Video) Then go ahead and Tweet it on the spot, it’s as Easy as 1,2,3, you also have the option to upload your album art that goes a long with that Song or Mixtape.Fans are going to consume what you have created in the very same way you intended them to use it.

Rhythmshare.com has created one of The best, easiest, and fastest ways for Musicians to be heard over the internet,you never know who is Listening out there, so go ahead and Share your Music With the World.
